#: ../../M/magic.rst:5
msgid "magic"
msgstr "magic"

#: ../../M/magic.rst:7
msgid ""
"adj. As yet unexplained, or too complicated to explain; compare "
":ref:`automagically` and (Arthur C.) Clarke's Third Law: \"Any sufficiently "
"advanced technology is indistinguishable from magic.\" \"TTY echoing is "
"controlled by a large number of magic bits.\" \"This routine magically "
"computes the parity of an 8-bit byte in three instructions.\""
msgstr ""
"形容詞 まだ説明されていない、あるいは説明するには複雑すぎる。\\ :ref:`automagically`\\ や(Arthur "
"C.)Clarkeの第三法則「十分に進歩した技術は魔法と見分けがつかない」と比較せよ。「TTYのエコーは多数のmagicなビットによって制御される」。「このルーチンは3命令で8ビットバイトのパリティをmagicに計算する」。"

#: ../../M/magic.rst:12
msgid ""
"adj. Characteristic of something that works although no one really "
"understands why (this is especially called :ref:`black-magic`\\)."
msgstr "形容詞 なぜかは誰も本当には理解していないが動くものの特性(これは特に\\ :ref:`black-magic`\\ と呼ばれる)。"

#: ../../M/magic.rst:15
msgid ""
"n\\. [Stanford] A feature not generally publicized that allows something "
"otherwise impossible, or a feature formerly in that category but now "
"unveiled."
msgstr ""
"名詞 [Stanford]一般には公表されていない、そうでなければ不可能なことを可能にする機能、あるいはかつてその範疇にあったが今や明かされた機能。"

#: ../../M/magic.rst:18
msgid ""
"n\\. The ultimate goal of all engineering & development, elegance in the "
"extreme; from the first corollary to Clarke's Third Law: \"Any technology "
"distinguishable from magic is insufficiently advanced\"."
msgstr "名詞 すべての工学と開発の究極の目標、極限の優雅さ。Clarkeの第三法則への第一系「魔法と見分けがつく技術は十分に進歩していない」から。"

#: ../../M/magic.rst:21
msgid ""
"Parodies playing on these senses of the term abound; some have made their "
"way into serious documentation, as when a MAGIC directive was described in "
"the Control Card Reference for GCOS c.1978. For more about hackish ‘magic’, "
"see :ref:`Appendix A<appendixa>`\\. Compare :ref:`black-magic`\\, "
":ref:`wizardly`\\, :ref:`deep-magic`\\, :ref:`heavy-wizardry`\\."
msgstr ""
"これらの語義にかけたパロディは多数あり、いくつかは真面目な文書に入り込んだ。1978年ごろのGCOSのControl Card "
"ReferenceでMAGICディレクティブが記述されたときのように。ハッカー的‘魔法’についてさらに知りたければ、\\ :ref:`Appendix "
"A<appendixa>`\\ を参照。\\ :ref:`black-magic`\\ 、\\ :ref:`wizardly`\\ 、\\ "
":ref:`deep-magic`\\ 、\\ :ref:`heavy-wizardry`\\ と比較せよ。"
